 />\n好易玩完又要換"},{"pid":"57cc957bc4d2ca6da8f9357f1a66c82bb0260957","tid":920631,"uid":65186,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T03:38:30.000Z","msg":"唔係等於颱風時玻璃黐膠紙？"},{"pid":"0d88a4bda2536c14f4f926409e4ebc99033edbbf","tid":920631,"uid":22553,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T03:44:27.000Z","msg":"用啲沙試下磨下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ad3304bb772fe3f12fad0e25fe9b5e273f64994","tid":920631,"uid":182786,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T03:46:37.000Z","msg":"淘寶20蚊支 汽車鍍膜, 唔想踢爆"},{"pid":"d1de9783c2eb4faf302457e7c6e1d3b8049de155","tid":920631,"uid":89882,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"57cc957bc4d2ca6da8f9357f1a66c82bb0260957","tid":920631,"uid":65186,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T03:38:30.000Z","msg":"唔係等於颱風時玻璃黐膠紙？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T03:47:12.000Z","msg":"要試過先知<br />\n一直都對納米呢樣野好有興趣<br />\n以前納米都係講緊咩件衫可以防水 滴啲水上去件衫 可以唔濕水就變成一滴一滴咁 細個覺得好神奇<br />\n宜家佢話做到防爆 想試下咩效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2705254e5c2eed96b5c932f9d3ccf453aa574d06","tid":920631,"uid":117975,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"81f405ea6fc0e682555e9589218d7092034f13fe","tid":920631,"uid":89882,"like":5,"dislike":7,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"2516b5fe63ea4a68e6f8d0adfb06a8d18cec37f0","tid":920631,"uid":117975,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T03:21:47.000Z","msg":"宜家納米啲技術真係發展得好快<br />\n乜野都防到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T03:27:12.000Z","msg":"本身見佢300幾蚊 咁撚貴<br />\n後尾見到佢原來用到係4部手機<br />\n圍番都係80幾蚊一條友<br />\n又好似幾抵屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T03:52:05.000Z","msg":"掂嘅又幾抵<br />\n邊度有得買先但係"},{"pid":"dbe8e8096b56a8b5696fc164171fb83a5a8874d0","tid":920631,"uid":63641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0